### 1. 查询所有用户（测试接口连通性）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/list

### 2. 注册用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "李四",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 登录成功
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "李四",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. 登录失败（密码错误）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "李四",
  "password": "123456789"
}

### 5. 注册重复用户名
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan",
  "password": "123789"
}